target: TEXT_CTSMJISTOCKYARDMANAGEMENT_00786_Q1_000_000<tab>探索を依頼する／開拓素材を受け取る
TEXT_CTSMJISTOCKYARDMANAGEMENT_00786_Q1_000_005<tab>「グラナリーオフィス」について聞く

source: TEXT_CTSMJISTOCKYARDMANAGEMENT_00786_OFFICER_000_000<tab>Where shall I send an expedition to next?
target:
TEXT_CTSMJISTOCKYARDMANAGEMENT_00786_OFFICER_000_000<tab>探索隊をどちらに派遣しますか？
収集先をご指定ください！

source: TEXT_CTSMJISTOCKYARDMANAGEMENT_00786_OFFICER_000_005<tab>We've just had a team return from an expedition! I have everything they gathered here, so be sure to collect the materials when you have a moment.
target:
TEXT_CTSMJISTOCKYARDMANAGEMENT_00786_OFFICER_000_005<tab>探索隊が帰還しました！
収集した開拓素材を保管しているので、
受け取りをお願いします！

source: TEXT_CTSMJISTOCKYARDMANAGEMENT_00786_OFFICER_100_000<tab>At the granary, you can dispatch a team of the finest mammet explorers to collect various materials from an area of your choosing. You just tell me where you want them to go, and I'll have them out there in a jiffy.
target:
TEXT_CTSMJISTOCKYARDMANAGEMENT_00786_OFFICER_100_000<tab>グラナリーオフィスでは、探索隊を派遣して、
開拓素材を集めることができます！
探索隊の派遣をご希望でしたら、お声がけください！

source: TEXT_CTSMJISTOCKYARDMANAGEMENT_00786_OFFICER_200_000<tab>A fellow explorer, I see. You're welcome to tour the island─erm, assuming you have the owner's permission─but I'm afraid the comings and goings of this facility are strictly confidential.
target:
TEXT_CTSMJISTOCKYARDMANAGEMENT_00786_OFFICER_200_000<tab>こんにちは！
こちらは島主様専用の施設のため、
お客様にはご利用いただけません……！

source: TEXT_CTSMJISTOCKYARDMANAGEMENT_00786_OFFICER_300_000<tab>That new cavern has been the talk of the isle! If you'd like, I can send a team down there to see what lucrative materials we can find.
target:
TEXT_CTSMJISTOCKYARDMANAGEMENT_00786_OFFICER_300_000<tab>あなたが洞窟への入口を見つけてくれたおかげで、
洞窟に、ぼくらの探索隊を派遣できるようになりました！
これからも無人島での生活に、ぼくらをお役立てくださいね！
